{"tid":2422310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"觀塘區議員鄧威文辦事處再遭「投籃式」淋糞水　狂徒避CCTV犯案","createTime":"2021-02-25T06:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T07:34:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4c94250d337a3c6deb86735b973d3845322872","tid":2422310,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210225/441597902125535232426183.jpeg/AKc6uponOWa3jzIMuXeuRiKvY9UfUvEcrcIK5K3CCuQ?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210225%2F441597902125535232426183.jpeg%2FAKc6uponOWa3jzIMuXeuRiKvY9UfUvEcrcIK5K3CCuQ%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=6e2cfc97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀塘區議員鄧威文的辦事處，再遭狂徒「投籃式」淋糞水。今日（25日）早上10時許，警方接獲報案指，秀茂坪邨秀和樓地下的鄧威文議員辦事處，後門遭狂徒淋糞水。據悉，狂徒曾踩線及看準閉路電視「死角位」犯案，疑犯用樽載着糞水，再拋進辨事處地面，職員揭發事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n現場可見，辦事處後門設有閉路電視系統，警員到場調查及翻查閉路電視片段，案件暫列刑事毀壞，暫未有人被捕。鄧威文的議員助理指，早於去年5月已有狂徒向後門掟屎，之後他們遂加裝閉路電視。連同今次事件，今個月已3度遭人淋糞水，目前仍不明兇徒的動機。<br />\n<br />\n鄧威文曾在今月10日，於其facebook專頁帖文指，有街坊捐贈的皮帶及衣物，被人淋水污染致損壞，「辦事處入伙接近10個月，門口被淋屎水兩次，後門倒貓砂加狗糞、雀仔屍體，到今次不明惡臭液體。」鄧的助理表示，本月初鄧威文發現有一批人士，於秀富樓及秀安樓對開位置聚賭。當時鄧威文曾勸止他們離開、避免違反限聚令，其間有人用粗言穢語指罵，更有人出手襲擊女助理，她事後送院檢驗。助理續稱，仍未知今次潑糞事件的因由。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，本港曾發生議員辦事處遭人狂徒抹屎案件。包括前年8月，時任葵青區議員梁錦威的辦事處，大門及外牆再發現被人抹屎，職員立即報警。同月，時任葵青區民主派區議員黃潤達，位於曉葵樓地下的辦事處亦曾三度遭潑糞，包括於門口門柄及地上遺下疑糞便，門口又被起「祭壇」。"},{"pid":"b0130d900af7181ba43ef85e3d1f1e337dfa1c67","tid":2422310,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d948d88d94aefef7288f6e1dcb42a2babd91215","tid":2422310,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"Dklm"},{"pid":"5544a7a4432b77f12b97609c10f040c925f9ec35","tid":2422310,"uid":71092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"有人犯法 就要執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50c30f257b1fe73f0d5b4530fc5a17ccbc97f50","tid":2422310,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5544a7a4432b77f12b97609c10f040c925f9ec35","tid":2422310,"uid":71092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"有人犯法 就要執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"藍屍唔計"},{"pid":"e978fad0a032d9624fd826f1f16955c2fb0b1ab5","tid":2422310,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"裝多兩支，呀公錢"},{"pid":"8ae428b581615d23f084967544dd5a16366d6d72","tid":2422310,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f50c30f257b1fe73f0d5b4530fc5a17ccbc97f50","tid":2422310,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5544a7a4432b77f12b97609c10f040c925f9ec35","tid":2422310,"uid":71092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"有人犯法 就要執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"藍屍唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"克警唔算"},{"pid":"b62af951bb28e247bf004c3e29307dbebe53ffa8","tid":2422310,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"班阿伯賭好大？"},{"pid":"d95c0db885547310c704a018e4f784e7b96a6949","tid":2422310,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf981283d07fa5909bb90f5b727f17adf32d5dc","tid":2422310,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor